  "full_text": "An update for util-linux is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe util-linux packages contain a large variety of low-level system utilities that are necessary for a Linux system to function. Among others, these include the fdisk configuration tool and the login program.Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s): lslogins dies querying the journal because of invalid use of sd_journal_get_data() API (JIRA:RHEL-117686)"
